📌 Project Overview

The dashboard provides a comprehensive view of sales trends, customer behavior, product performance, and regional analysis. It helps identify growth opportunities, top-performing categories, and areas needing improvement through clear visual storytelling and dynamic reporting.

🛠 Tools & Technologies Used
Power BI
Power Query
DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
Excel / CSV Dataset
Data Cleaning & Transformation
Data Modeling
Data Visualization


📊 Key Features
Daily, Weekly, and Monthly Sales Trend Analysis
Revenue and Profit Performance Tracking
Top-Selling Products and Categories Analysis
Customer Segmentation Insights
Regional and State-wise Sales Performance
Interactive Filters and Drill-through Analysis
KPI Cards for Quick Business Overview
Dynamic Dashboard for real-time decision support


📈 Business Insights Generated
Identified high-performing products contributing maximum revenue
Analyzed customer purchase patterns across different regions
Detected underperforming categories requiring strategic improvement
Compared monthly growth trends for better forecasting
Improved understanding of customer segmentation for targeted marketing
🎯 Project Objective

To transform raw ecommerce sales data into meaningful insights using Power BI and help businesses make strategic decisions related to sales optimization, customer targeting, and operational efficiency.

